 flycatcher]]<br/>(''Ficedula albicollis'') ||<center>[[File:Mucho\u0142\u00f3wka bia\u0142oszyja (samiec).jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A rare vagrant\n|-\n| [[European pied flycatcher|Pied flycatcher]]<br/>(''Ficedula hypoleuca'') ||<center>[[File:Ficedula hypoleuca -Wood of Cree Nature Reserve, Scotland -male-8a.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A breeding summer visitor\n|-\n| [[Black redstart]]<br/>(''Phoenicurus ochruros'') ||<center>[[File:Hausrotschwanz Brutpflege 2006-05-21-05.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A scarce breeding resident, passage migrant & winter visitor\n|-\n| [[Common redstart]]<br/>(''Phoenicurus phoenicurus'') ||<center>[[File:Gekraagde Roodstaart 20040627.JPG|500x160px]]</center> || A breeding summer visitor\n|-\n| [[Moussier's redstart]]<br/>(''Phoenicurus moussieri'') ||<center>[[File:Phoenicurus moussieri.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A rare vagrant\n|-\n| [[Common rock thrush|Rock thrush]]<br/>(''Monticola saxatilis'') ||<center>[[File:Monsax.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A rare vagrant\n|-\n| [[Blue rock thrush]]<br/>(''Monticola solitarius'') ||<center>[[File:BlueRockTrush LaCanada.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A rare vagrant\n|-\n| [[Whinchat]]<br/>(''Saxicola rubetra'') ||<center>[[File:Saxicola rubetra -Belgium -male-8.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A breeding summer visitor & passage migrant\n|-\n| [[Siberian stonechat]]<br/>(''Saxicola maurus'') ||<center>[[File:Siberian Stonechat (Saxicola maura)- Male at Bharatpur I IMG 5768.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A rare vagrant\n|-\n| [[European stonechat]]<br/>(''Saxicola rubicola'') ||<center>[[File:European Stonechat.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A resident breeding species \n|-\n| [[Isabelline wheatear]]<br/>(''Oenanthe isabellina'') ||<center>[[File:Isabelline wheatear (Oenanthe isabellina) male, non-breeding.jpg|500x160px]]</center> || A rare vagrant\n|-\n| [[Northern wheatear]]<br/>(''Oenanthe oenanthe'') ||<center>[[File:Northern wheatear male09.JPG|500x160px]]</center> || A breeding summer visitor & 