31}}<ref name=\"Birthday\"/><ref name=\"IndianExpress\"/>\n| birth_place        = [[Malerkotla]], [[Punjab, India|Punjab]], [[India]]\n| spouse             = {{marriage|Heena Iqbal|2017}}\n| children           = 1\n| relatives          = [[Mohammad Nazim]] (cousin)\n| residence          = \n| occupation         = Actor\n| nationality        = Indian\n| yearsactive        = 2006\u2013present\n| known_for          = [[Diya Aur Baati Hum]]<br>[[Dharti Ka Veer Yodha Prithviraj Chauhan]]\n}}\n\n'''Anas Rashid''' is an Indian television actor who works in the [[Indian soap opera]]s. He rose to fame for portraying the [[Prithviraj Chauhan|eponymous character]] [[Prithviraj Chauhan]] in the historical drama ''[[Dharti Ka Veer Yodha Prithviraj Chauhan]]'' (2006\u201309) and ''Sooraj Rathi'' in the soap opera ''[[Diya Aur Baati Hum]]'', which ranked among the [[Top 10 Indian Television Serials|highest-rated Indian television series]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/2015-04-07/Party-all-night-for-the-team-of-Diya-Aur-Baati-Hum-142461|title=Party all night for the team of Diya Aur Baati Hum!|website=The Hans India|access-date=31 July 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512180921/http://www.thehansindia.com/posts/index/2015-04-07/Party-all-night-for-the-team-of-Diya-Aur-Baati-Hum-142461|archive-date=12 May 2017|url-status=live|date=7 April 2015}}</ref><ref name=\":1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/gecs/shashi-sumeet-productions-diya-aur-baati-hum-completes-3-glorious-years-140902|title=Shashi Sumeet Productions' Diya Aur Baati Hum completes 3 glorious years|date=2 September 2014|website=Indian Television Dot Com|accessdate=15 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916223136/http://www.indiantelevision.com/television/tv-channels/gecs/shashi-sumeet-productions-diya-aur-baati-hum-completes-3-glorious-years-140902|archive-date=16 September 2018|url-status=live}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Aamir Khan visits Sandhya and Suraj on the show ''Diya Aur Baati Hum'' |url=http://www.apunkachoice.com/content/slide_show/sid100009222-pics_aamir_khan_visits_sandhya_and_suraj_on_the_show_diya_aur_baati_hum/ |work=www.apunkachoice.com|accessdate=12 December 2012 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120703224321/http://www.apunkachoice.com/content/slide_show/sid100009222-pics_aamir_khan_visits_sandhya_and_suraj_on_the_show_diya_aur_baati_hum/ |archivedate=3 July 2012  }}</ref>\n\n==Early life==\nRashid was born in [[Malerkotla]] into a conservative Muslim family.<ref name=Birthday/><ref name=\":0\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/television/celebrity/story/remember-diya-aur-baati-hum-s-anas-rashid-you-will-be-surprised-to-know-what-he-s-doing-now-1301281-2018-07-31|title=Remember Diya Aur Baati Hum's Anas Rashid? You will be surprised to know what he's doing now|last=|first=|date=|website=India Today|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> He has two brothers and two sisters. He did his schooling from an Urdu Medium School and has done his post-graduation in Psychology. He is fluent in Urdu, Arabic and Persian languages. He is also a well trained singer. He also won the title of Mr. Punjab in 2004.<ref name=Birthday/> His cousins are television actors [[Mohammad Nazim]] and Ather Habib.<ref>{{cite news |title=10 unknown interesting facts about Mohammad Nazim |url=http://www.tellychakkar.com/tv/features/10-unknown-interesting-facts-about-mohammad-nazim-548 |accessdate=4 March 2019 |work=TellyChakkar |author=TellychakkarTeam |date=8 April 2014}}</ref>{{better source|reason=Source is considered unreliable as per [[WP:ICTF]]|date=March 2019}}\n\n==Career==\nRashid made his screen debut with the [[Star Plus]] drama ''[[Kahiin To Hoga]]'' as Kartik Ahluwalia.<ref name=\":2\">{{Cite web|url=https://m.timesofindia.com/tv/news/hindi/My-career-started-as-a-joke-Anas-Rashid/articleshow/16514988.cms|title=My career started as a joke: Anas Rashid|last=|first=|date=|website=Times of India|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> He went on to feature in a supporting role in the drama ''[[Aise Karo Naa Vidaa]]''. However, his breakthrough role was the portrayal of [[Prithviraj Chauhan]], in the historical drama ''[[Dharti Ka Veer Yodha Prithviraj Chauhan]]'' on Star Plus, which made him a household name in India.<ref name=\":2\" /> Anas worked as the male lead in ''[[Diya Aur Baati Hum]]'', where he portrayed the role of Sooraj Rathi.<ref name=\":0\" /> Rashid also marked his singing debut with one of the series song. ''Diya Aur Baati Hum'' ranked among the [[Top 10 Indian Television Serials|highest-rated Indian television serials]]. His performance in the series earned him wide recognition as well as several accolades.<ref>{{cite web|title=Anas Rashid turns singer on TV show|url=http://www.indiawest.com/entertainment/television/diya-aur-baati-hum-deepika-singh-and-anas-rashid-bury/article_4ca9f1f6-c8f4-11e4-8cb7-7bd7e031597a.html|date=1 October 2015|access-date=27 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809073136/http://www.indiawest.com/entertainment/television/diya-aur-baati-hum-deepika-singh-and-anas-rashid-bury/article_4ca9f1f6-c8f4-11e4-8cb7-7bd7e031597a.html|archive-date=9 August 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name=\"IndianExpress\">{{cite web|title=Anas Rashid turns singer on TV show |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/television/anas-rashid-turns-singer-on-tv-show/|work=indianexpress.com|date=12 March 2015|access-date=27 October 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151028163335/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/television/anas-rashid-turns-singer-on-tv-show/|archive-date=28 October 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nIn 2018, he made his feature film debut in the Punjabi film ''[[Nankana (film)|Nankana]]'' starring [[Gurdas Maan]].<ref name=\":3\">{{Cite web|url=https://m.hindustantimes.com/tv/anas-rashid-on-tv-comeback-i-want-to-play-a-character-with-grey-shades/story-C0By4mCO5V6YyU8AsQFn0L.html|title=Anas Rashid on TV comeback: I want to play a character with grey shades|last=|first=|date=4 March 2018|website=Hindustan Times|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n==Personal life==\nRashid married Heena Iqbal, a corporate professional from [[Chandigarh]], in 2017.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ndtv.com/entertainment/anas-rashid-is-complete-and-content-after-marrying-heena-1749738|title=Anas Rashid Is 'Complete And Content' After Marrying Heena|last=|first=|date=|website=NDTV|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref> They have a daughter named Aayat, born in 2019.<ref>{{cite news |title=Diya Aur Baati Hum actor Anas Rashid shares the first picture of his baby girl Aayat |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/hindi/diya-aur-baati-hum-actor-anas-rashid-shares-the-first-picture-of-his-baby-girl-aayat/articleshow/67986616.cms |accessdate=5 March 2019 |work=[[The Times of India]] |date=14 February 2019}}</ref>\n\n== Television works ==\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 106%;\" border=\"2\" cellpadding=\"4\" background: #f9f9f9;\n|- align=\"center\"\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Year(s)\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |Show\n! style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" | Role\n!style=\"background:#B0C4DE;\" |Notes\n!References\n|-\n| 2006\u201307\n| ''[[Kahiin To Hoga]]''\n| Kartik Ahluwalia\n|\n|<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-\n| 2006\u201307\n| ''[[Kyaa Hoga Nimmo Kaa]]''\n| Karan Sehgal\n| \n|<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-\n| 2006\u201309\n| ''[[Dharti Ka Veer Yodha Prithviraj Chauhan]]''\n| [[Prithviraj Chauhan]]\n|\n|<ref name=\":2\" />\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Aise Karo Naa Vidaa]]''\n| Prince Yashwardha\n| \n|<ref name=\":3\" />\n|-\n| 2011\u20132016\n| ''[[Diya Aur Baati Hum]]''\n| rowspan =2| Sooraj Rathi\n|\n|<ref name=\":1\" />\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Tu Sooraj, Main Saanjh Piyaji]]''\n| Guest appearance\n|<ref>{{Ci